Umubare w'abantu banduye coronavirus (COVID-19) mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, wazamutse guhera ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) kigaragaza ko ibintu bimeze nk'uko mu muryango w'ibihugu by'i Burayi/agace k'ubukungu k'i Burayi n'u Bwongereza bikagaragaza ko nubwo bimeze mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe bigomba kurushaho kwitegura kwakira umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazahabwa ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu bitaro by'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya pneumonia cyo mu bwoko butaramenyekana cyatangijwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa cyo kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko virusi ya coronavirus nshya ari indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze cyane ya coronavirus 2 (SARS-COV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cyazanywe n'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 cyiswe coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko abantu 80% banduye COVID-19 bafite indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'ibyorezo by'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite umusonga, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu barwayi 14%, COVID-19 igenda irushaho kuba indwara ikomeye isaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro mu gihe mu barwayi 6% igenda irushaho kuba indwara ikomeye isaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro byabugenewe.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro bazira COVID-19 wari kuri 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turagenzura impinduka mu mibare ya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) na Ubwongereza (UK) tukayigereranya n'iy'intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cyo ku ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU / EEA no mu Bwongereza
Uretse mu Bushinwa, COVID-19 ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu bitandukanye kandi ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 ku isi yose ubu bukurikiraho iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nyandiko yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020 ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko mu Burayi ari ho habonetse bwa mbere umuntu wafashweho icyorezo cya COVID-19 hashingiwe ku byavuye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na OMS.
Muri EU/EEA, u Bufaransa bwatangaje abantu batatu ba mbere banduye coronavirus ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bigize EU/EEA ndetse n'u Bwongereza, aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'iyo tariki, abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye 1,727 bari bamaze gutangazwa, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hari abantu 17,750 banduye n'abapfuye 1,441.
Gukusanya no gukusanya amakuru ku byerekeye icyorezo cya COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no kurwanya indwara (ECDC), cyatangaje ko imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, itangwa n'ibigo by'ubuzima by'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima mpuzamahanga na OMS, buri munsi ihita ivugururwa saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma ibipimo bya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Aherero Shyanga na UK, no kubigereranya n'iby'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'igereranyo cy'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19, twabaze iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, bityo tuzirikana icyerekezo cya COVID-19, muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, hagati ya 1 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twanabagejejeho kandi umubare w'ibarura ry'abatangajwe ko banduye mu bihugu byose ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa ugereranyije n'abatangajwe ko banduye mu Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uburyo COVID-19 yifashisha mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Mu minsi 14 ishize, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza wazamutseho inshuro ebyiri, aho mu Bushinwa ari mu ntara ya Hubei (Ifoto 1).
Ku bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi na Ubwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abandura COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma uzamuka cyane ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibishushanyo mbonera).
Ibi byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'umubare w'abatangaza ko banduye mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza na byo byatangaje ko byongereye umubare w'abandura COVID-19 (Umutwaro w'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Byerekana ko, guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani z'amanywa, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'i Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza byari bimaze gutangaza ko byanduye mu gihe kingana n'icya Butaliyani, mu byumweru 3 cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abandura COVID-19 uri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibitegerejwe ku byabaye mu gihe cya COVID-19 byerekana ko icyorezo cyateye mu bihugu byose mu buryo bwihuse.
Ibi kandi birimo kuba ibihugu biri mu bihe bitandukanye, mu bisubizo by'ubuzima rusange ku rwego rw'igihugu, ndetse n'uburyo bwo gupima biratandukanye mu bihugu no mu buryo butandukanye bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa ngo harebwe niba bafite COVID-19, harimo no kuba bapimwa.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twazahajwe n'icyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko hafi 10% by'abarwayi barwaye COVID-19 bari bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwimbitse, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwimbitse muri utwo turere byari bimaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo busanzwe.
Amakuru ajyanye no kuvurwa kwa COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu cyumba cy'indembe, ubu aboneka ku rwego rw'ibihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA ku barwayi 6% na 1% gusa, bakurikije uko bakurikirana (amakuru ntiyagaragajwe).
Icyakora, zigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo zihuze n'amakuru y'ubugenzuzi bw'ubu, yibanze ku gutanga amakuru y'ubwandu n'imfu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu kubona ibitaro by'indembe n'ibitanda by'indembe i Burayi, kuva kuri 29.2 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4.2 ku baturage 100.000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo muto cyangwa ukaba muto ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ubuvuzi bwihariye n'ibitaro by'ubuvuzi ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Imibare y'ibanze ishingiye ku kwiyongera kw'ibigo nderabuzima, ingano ya buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'iy'u Bwongereza n'umubare w'abajyanwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 bahura n'ibyago byo kurwara birenze 90% by'abarembye, byatanzwe mu bushakashatsi bwa gatandatu bw'ikigo ECDC ku ngorane za COVID-19.
Kubera ko ubwandu bwiyongereye cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe by'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA na Ubwongereza, ibitaro n'ibigo by'inderabare akenshi bifasha abaturage bo mu karere bizwi, amakuru y'ibipimo by'indwara n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi byashoboka ko yaboneka ku rwego rwa Nomenclature y'ibice by'igihugu by'ibarura 2 (NUTS-2).
Inyigisho zaturutse mu Butaliyani n'ibikomeje kugaragara mu bindi bihugu byerekanye ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe bigomba kwitegura guhangana n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwiyongera k'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, no kwitabwaho byihariye, nk'uko bimeze mu turere twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi buheruka bwakozwe na ECDC, ibikorwa byihuta, byuzuye kandi byuzuye ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, hamwe no kuva ku buryo bwihuta cyane ku cyorezo ukajya ku cyorezo, kuko kwiyongera kwihuse kw'umubare w'abandura bishobora gutuma abaganga n'ibitaro bihabwa igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no gushyiraho ingamba mbere y'igihe.
Igenzura ryibanze ry'ibyago ryashyizeho ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito cyane ibihugu bifite cyo kongera ingufu mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo by'uburwayi.
Ibyo birimo kuvuga ko, bishoboka ko gahunda z'ubuvuzi z'ibindi bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi na EEA zishobora kuzahura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi n'ibyumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), giterwa n'indwara y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu imaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 ikagira abasaga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no ku isi hose, yabaye icyorezo cyugarije ikiremwamuntu.
Kimwe n'agakoko gatera indwara ya SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu ibihumbi n'ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kandi kwandurwa n'inzige kandi igatuma umuntu agira ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Nyamara, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ingaruka nkeya ugereranyije na SARS ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka ku bantu benshi bakuze kurusha abakiri bato no ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Kubera ibisubizo ku gipimo cyihuta cyo gutangaza kuri virusi, iyi ngingo yagerageje gutanga isesengura ryimbitse ry'iterambere ry'ibanze ry'ubushakashatsi.
Tuziga ibintu by'ibanze byerekeye indwara zandura, indwara z'ibyorezo, indwara z'ibyorezo, uburyo bwo kuzisuzuma, uburyo bwo kuvurwa, uburyo bwo kuzibura no kwirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bigikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iki kiganiro cyafashije mu gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara iteje akaga.
Ibirori by'impeshyi ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 byabaye ibirori bitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo muri ibi biruhuko byose ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma y'icyorezo.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara ikomeye ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero (SARS) mu 2003; bityo, Ishami ry'Isi ry'Ubuzima (WHO) ryayise SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, naho virusi ifitanye isano nayo yitwa CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gihita gikwirakwira mu gihugu cyose no mu bindi bihugu 50 ku isi.
Kuva ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi itera COVID-19 imaze kwemeza abantu barenga 80.000, abarwayi basaga 40.000 bakaba barakize, naho abarwayi basaga 3.000 bakaba barapfuye.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi w'abantu ku isi" ufite imbaraga kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zirenga 200 ku COVID-19 zashyizwe ahagaragara harimo virusi, indwara, impamvu, gusuzuma no kuvura kuva raporo ya mbere ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje ko icyorezo cyashyizwe mu kato n'abarwayi benshi.
Iyi nteguro igerageza kwerekana ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi mu cyiciro gishya kandi gihindagurika vuba cy'ibikoresho.
Mu gihe bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi CoV yatewe n'iyi virusi, indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo mu cyarabu (MERS, mu 2012).
Tuzasuzuma kandi ibyo twize kugeza ubu ku bijyanye no kwirinda no guteza indwara ndetse n'ibindi bibazo bikiriho.
Ubusanzwe, za CoVs zifatwa nk'indwara zidakora ku bantu, kuko zangiza 15% by'indwara y'ibicurane 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'indwara ebyiri z'abantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi zihita zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu zikagira ingaruka mbi n'urupfu.
Ni yo mpamvu, COVID-19 iriho ubu ari icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa mu ishusho.1,1, icyorezo cya pneumonia itagira inkomoko cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 cyabanje kumenyekana mu kigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, basuzumye imiterere ya CoV.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, habonetse umuntu wa mbere wanduye indwara ivuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, iyo ndwara yakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, mu ntara no mu bihugu byo hafi aho.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, raporo y'abaganga yagaragaje ko bishoboka ko umuntu umwe ashobora kwandurira undi.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wari wafunzwe kandi ingendo rusange zirahagarikwa.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze ku cyorezo bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bagaragayeho ubwandu, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye n'isoko ryo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ryagurishwagamo ibyokurya byo mu nyanja, aho bivugwa ko ari ho ha mbere havuye ubwandu bw'iyo ndwara buturuka ku nyamaswa.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cyabayeho mu buryo bwihutirwa ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyi virusi yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose (Igice cya (Igice cya 2).2)
Mu gihe iki cyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera, nta wuzi uko kizarangira n'uko kizarushaho gukwirakwira.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo ku barwayi 8,866, barimo 4,021 bemeje ko banduye COVID-19, bwasohoye amakuru mashya y'icyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS ifata abantu bo mu myaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu bafite hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abantu banduye, bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, bake bari munsi y'imyaka 20, naho 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ifata cyane abagabo (0.31 / 100,000) kurusha abagore (0.27 / 100,000).
COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye cyane muri Hubei no mu nkengero zayo.
COVID-19 ifata iminsi 5 (2-9) kuva ku munsi ya mbere kugeza ku munsi wa nyuma yo gusuzumwa.
Igihe cy'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu ni iminsi 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
