Yavuze ko hakiri byinshi byo kumenya kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga ku kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu gusubiza iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangijwe gahunda yihutirwa yo kurinda ibinyabuzima.
Nubwo ibikorwa byo kwishyiriraho abimukira mu modoka byamaze gukorwa mu bice bitandukanye by'igihugu, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gahunda yo gucyura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba ambasade babyo mu bihugu by'amahanga, mbere na mbere hakoreshejwe gari ya moshi, abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bakaba bemerewe kuva mu gihugu.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byatangije gahunda yo guhashya abaturage babyo.
Pakistan ivuga ko itazongera kwirukana abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, igihugu cya Brezili cyirukanye abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili, harimo n'Abashinwa bane n'Umuhindi umwe.
Abaturage ba Polonye, Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde basohotse mu ndege bari muri Polonye mu gihe indege yabo yari igeze muri Brezili yari ihagaritse igamije kuruhuka.
Abaturage ba Brezili bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare hafi ya Brasilia.
Mu munsi umwe, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ya kabiri ya Leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan berekezwa mu kigo cya Trenton CFB, aho bari kumara ibyumweru bibiri mu kato.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abantu 185 ba Kanada bari bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan yageze ku kibuga cy'indege cya CFB Trenton.
Abakozi ba Ositaraliya bakuye abaturage 277 ku kirwa cya Christmas Island mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 kuva ku itariki ya 3 kugeza ku ya 4 Gashyantare.
Indege yari iturutse muri Nouvelle Zelande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo n'abaturutse muri Ositaraliya na Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku cyambu cya Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, leta ya Amerika yatangaje ko igiye gutabara abaturage bayo ikoresheje ubwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi b'Abanyakanada 129 bari bavuye muri Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, ubwato bw'indege ya Afrika y'Epfo bwashinzwe na guverinoma y'Afurika y'Epfo bwahitanye abantu 112 b'abimukira.
Mbere yo kugenda, abagenzi bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragayeho ibimenyetso bya Coronavirus basuzumwe n'abaganga, ariko barekerwa nyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo bari bafite icyorezo cy'ibicurane byemejwe ko ari bo bakirwaye, boherejwe mu bihugu byabo.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini byakozwe ku Banyafurika bose, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abakozi bo mu ndege, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bagize uruhare mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi, bose bashyizwe mu kato kandi bari mu kato k'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo cy'iyi ndwara.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusi, Pakistani, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bahuriye hamwe kugira ngo bafashe mu kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe n'icyorezo, hamwe n'itsinda ry'ubufatanye mu gace ka Chicago bivugwa ko ryatumye udupfukamunwa 50.000 twa N95 mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi utegamiye kuri Leta, ku bufatanye na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho byo kwirinda, harimo udupfukamunwa n'udupfukamunwa n'ibikoresho, hakoreshejwe indege z'ubutabazi mu buryo bwihutirwa ku bitaro bya Wuhan ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari yo gufasha OMS mu rwego rwo gutanga imiti, ubuvuzi ndetse no kurinda indwara mu bihugu byo muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'amajyepfo, aho iyi virusi igeze mu bantu benshi.
Interaksys yatangaje ko Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yoherereje Filipine inkunga y'udupfukamunwa 200,000 ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, umuryango utabara w'Abanyarwandakazi muri Singapuru watangaje ko ugiye kohereza imfashanyo y'amadolari y'u Bushinwa angana na miliyoni 2.26.
U Buyapani bwahaye Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwoherereje Wuhan toni zisaga 13 z'imfashanyo, Maleziya yatangaje ko yahaye u Bushinwa miliyoni 18 z'imiti, u Budage bwatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, ndetse na Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, ndetse yemeye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'inyongera mu nkunga y'amafaranga ku bihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko ibintu bisa n'ibisubiranye mu Bushinwa, u Bushinwa bwatangiye kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byahuye n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba, Uburusiya byohereje imfashanyo z'ibikoresho n'imiti byo gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima byibuze miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro yo kwirinda 60,000 i Addis Ababa, Ethiopia kugira ngo byatangwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho 5000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100.000 n'ibyuma bitanu byo guhumeka muri Panama.
Yatanze kandi imiti muri Kanada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'imyenda yo mu maso n'ibikoresho byo gupima.
Espagne yahagaritse ibikoresho 58,000 byo gupima coronavirus byo mu Bushinwa, bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30%, naho Ubuholandi bwasubije udupfukamunwa 600,000 twari twanduye.
Ububiligi bwibutse udupfukamunwa 100.000 tudakoreshwa twiyumvagamo ko twaturutse mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije gahunda yo gufasha ibihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye cyane ibikorwa by'abayobozi b'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya icyorezo.
"OMS ivuga ko hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu mwaka wa 2002 - 2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwa kuba barashyize ahagaragara amakuru y'ibanga yabangamiye ibikorwa byo gukumira no gukumira, n'icyorezo gihari ubu aho ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa "butanga amakuru mashya buri munsi kugira ngo birinde guhangayika mbere y'iminsi mikuru yo mu mwaka mushya. " "
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku ngingo z'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu zo guhagarika ingendo, Gauden Galea, umuyobozi wa OMS, yavuze ko "mu by'ukuri, iyi ntambwe itari imwe mu ngamba za OMS zo guhagarika ingendo, kandi ko ari intambwe ikomeye yo guteza akaga ku ngendo". Yavuze ko iyi ari impanuka mu mateka y'ubuzima. Nyuma yo kwemeza ko mu Bushinwa habonetse abantu banduye icyorezo cya kanseri ku ya 30 Mutarama, hamwe n'umubare w'abanduye wiyongera mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingutu cyibasiye ubuzima bw'abaturage, kikaba ari icya gatandatu cyatangajwe nyuma y'icyorezo cya kanseri y'ingurube mu mwaka wa 2009.[1]
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko iki cyorezo cyatangijwe nk'icyorezo cy'indwara z'indwara z'indwara rusange zihutirwa ku bihugu bitewe n'ingaruka z'icyorezo, cyane cyane ku bihugu bikennye n'ibigo nderabuzima.
Mu gusubiza ku ngingo yo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yatangaje ko "nta mpamvu yo guhagarika ingendo z'abantu ku giti cyabo, mu rwego rwo kubangamira ubucuruzi n'ingendo mpuzamahanga". Yongeyeho ko OMS idatanga inama ku guhagarika ingendo, guhagarika ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingendo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye ibihugu byo ku isi inkunga ingana na miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika yo gufasha ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo mu bihugu bikennye, isaba ko ibihugu bidafite ingamba zihari zo guhangana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 byakwihutira gufasha mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dufite imbaraga mu gihe dufite intege nkeya", asaba ibindi bihugu gukora byihuse kugira ngo birinde ingaruka mbi mu gihe kiri imbere. Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, yatangaje ko icyorezo cyiswe COVID-19.
Umunsi umwe, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gutanga imbaraga zose z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyo gitero.
"Itsinda ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye rishinzwe kurwanya ibiza ryashyizweho, ryemerera ko habaho uburyo bw'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, aho ibihugu bya OMS bishobora "gushyira imbaraga mu gusubiza mu rwego rw'ubuzima mu gihe ibindi bihugu bishobora gutanga ubuhanga bwabyo mu gufasha abaturage, ubukungu n'iterambere, bikerekana ko icyorezo gikomeje gukwirakwira cyane".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba OMS riyobowe n'abashinwa ryatangiriye ibikorwa byo gukangurira abashinwa mu Bushinwa gukwirakwiza icyorezo mu gihugu bakorana inama n'abayobozi b'igihugu no gusura abaturage kugira ngo bakomeze ibikorwa by'ubutabazi mu turere tw'icyaro, mu mijyi ndetse no mu cyaro. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko Isi yose yiteguye icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora kuba, ariko ko igihugu kitarigeze kigera ku rwego rw'icyorezo, nta mpamvu yo gutangira ibikorwa by'ubutabazi.
Mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo, OMS yashyizeho itsinda ryihariye ry'abagenzuzi. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS batangaje ko coronavirus ishobora kuba yibasiye isi yose, bityo ko ari cyo gihe cy'icyorezo gikomeye.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ubuzima ya OMS, yaburiye mu itangazo ko, "Iki ari icyemezo cy'ukuri kuri buri leta ku isi: Kanguka".
"Iyi virusi ishobora kuba igiye kuza kandi ugomba guhora witeguye, "" bavuga ko ingamba zikwiye zafasha isi kwirinda"" icyorezo cyayo kiruta ibindi byose. ""
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atuma inzego z'ubuzima zidashobora kwemeza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi, ko iri tangazo risobanura ko "cyane cyane ko twemera ko umuntu wese ku isi ashobora guhura n'iki cyorezo".
OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe.
"Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS ihangayikishijwe cyane n'uburyo iyi virusi ikwirakwira, ubukana bwayo, n'umutekano muke w'iki cyorezo. " OMS yahawe impaka zikomeye z'uko nta muti uhagije ihari, harimo no gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima bw'abaturage, no gushyira iyi virusi mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo".
Abashinjacyaha barimo kandi batanze inyandiko yo gusaba Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, gutanga imihoho, yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 kuva ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere nyinshi z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zashyize imbaraga mu kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishyaka ry'abasivili rivuga ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kwivuna kandi ko ibi bizakorwa mu buryo bwumvikana.
Iri shyirahamwe ryashimangiye ko kubura ibintu by'ibanze cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba kuba impamvu yo gupfobya itsinda ry'abantu badafite ubwenegihugu.
Impuguke zigaragaza ko uburenganzira bw'ubuzima bwa muntu butandukanye kuva ku bafite ubumuga, abakene, abatishoboye, impunzi, abatishoboye n'abandi bantu bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga y'ubutegetsi irimo guhangana n'ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage zatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubumwe n'Iterambere ry'Ubukungu watangije gahunda yo gutanga amakuru ku gihe ku bikorwa n'ibyifuzo by'ibihugu by'amahanga.
Uhereye ku ngamba zo gushimangira gahunda z'ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi hose kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibikoresho bya konti n'ibihano ku ngendo, umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga washyize hamwe na Politiki y'Igihugu, hagamijwe gufasha ibihugu kwigira kuri buri kimwe no korohereza ingamba zo guhangana na coronavirus ku isi hose.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yanenze cyane Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubwongereza Michael Gove, Perezida wa Burezili Eduardo Bolsonaro na Jair Bolsonaro, kubera icyorezo cy'icyorezo cyadutse mu Bushinwa mu ntara ya Hubei.
Abayobozi benshi bo mu ntara mu ishyaka ry'abakominisitiri b'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanwe kubera uburyo bakoresheje ibikorwa byaryo mu Bushinwa rwagati, ikimenyetso kigaragaza ko batishimiye uburyo politiki yashyizweho mu gihe cy'icyorezo cyugarije uturere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagaragaje ko ibi bikorwa byakozwe mu rwego rwo kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping kurakara kwa rubanda kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Abakozi bamwe bo mu Bushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, batangajwe ko banduye icyorezo cya COVID-19 i Wuhan, nyuma yo kwandura muri Amerika no mu Butaliyani.
Guverinoma ya Donald Trump ya Amerika yise coronavirus "virusi y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan" ivuga ko "mu gihe gito, virusi yateye ikagera ku rwego rw'icyorezo ku isi", naho abandi bayobozi bayigamba ko ari ivangura rishingiye ku moko kandi ko "yatewe n'uko guverinoma ye yananiwe kurwanya icyo cyorezo".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyafashe televiziyo ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu gihe cy'ikiganiro cyagaragazaga gahunda y'igikorwa cy'ubutasi cy'Inteko y'Igihugu ishinzwe umutekano, kivuga ko hari ikiganiro cyavuze ko "Ibitekerezo by'Abanyamerika byerekeza ku Bushinwa".
Twahawe inama yo kugerageza gukwirakwiza ubwo butumwa mu buryo bumwe cyangwa ubundi, harimo ibiterane by'abanyamakuru, ibiganiro bya televiziyo, imyigaragambyo ya politiki, politiki y'amahanga, kandi Bloomberg yari ifite intego yo kugerageza kohereza inkunga mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo mu rugendo rwo kwigarurira ibicuruzwa ku isi.
Perezida w'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Josep Borell, yaburiye ko politiki y'akarere irimo intambara yo gushaka ubutegetsi binyuze mu buryo bw'amacakubiri n'imyifatire yo kwiba.
Borrel yakomeje avuga ko Ubushinwa bugerageza gutanga ubutumwa ko butandukanye na Amerika, ko ari inshuti y'ukuri kandi yiringirwa.
Ubushinwa bwasabye Amerika kureka gukurikiza amategeko yashyizeho kuri Siriya, Venezuela na Irani, kandi itera inkunga ibihugu bibiri bya mbere.
Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zahagaritse inkunga ya Jack Ma y'impu 100,000 yoherezwa muri Cuba n'itegeko rya Amerika ryo ku ya 3 Mata.
Abayobozi ba Amerika barashinjwa ko bahindura imikorere y'ibihugu byabo mu gihe cyo gushyigikira ibihugu byabo.
Hari n'impaka ku ikoreshwa ry'udupfukamunwa mu bihugu bitandukanye, harimo u Budage, Otirishiya na Suisse; Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Turukiya yafashe kandi ibyuma byinshi bya poroteyine by'umwuka byari kugezwa muri Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yahakanye inama y'ibihugu by'i Burayi ivuga ko ntacyo yakoze mu gihe iki cyorezo cyakwirakwijwe mu gihugu.
Ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani muri EU, Maurizio Massari, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwitabiriye icyo kibazo".
"Ntabwo ari ikimenyetso cyiza cyo guhuza uburayi. """
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo guterefona na Minisitiri w'intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yateguye ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza mu Butaliyani imiti ya gisirikare, imodoka zihariye z'intambara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani La Stampa cyasohoye ingingo ikomeye ivuga ko 80% by'ubufasha bw'u Burusiya "butagira akamaro cyangwa nta nyungu bufitiye u Butaliyani".
Iri tangazo ryashinje Uburusiya gushyigikira politiki y'akarere n'intwaro za gipolitiki zangiza.
Perezida w'intara ya Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ubutaliyani ushinzwe ububanyi n'amahanga, Luigi Di Maio, bahakanye ibyo itangazamakuru ryavuze kandi bagaragaza ko bishimiye ibyo bagezeho.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara imizigo irimo ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko mu gihe abakozi ba leta ya Putin bari gufashwa muri Amerika, [Putin] yavuze ko mu gihe inganda z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika zari kuba zikomeye, bashoboraga gusubiza ibicuruzwa mu gihugu bibaye ngombwa.
Igisirikare cya NATO ""Defender 2020"" cy'intambara mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu byo mu karere ka Baltique, ni cyo gikorwa cya gisirikare kinini cya NATO cyakozwe kuva Intambara y'Ubutita yarangira, kizakorwa mu buryo bugabanya ingano y'ingabo.
Umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ryo kurwanya ikoreshwa ry'intwaro kirimbuzi Kate Hudson yanenze bimwe mu byemezo byafashwe mu 2020. Yavuze ko ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange cyibasiye abasirikare ba Amerika n'abandi bo mu Burayi ndetse n'abaturage bo mu bihugu abasirikare bakoreramo.  Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyibasiye cyane guverinoma ya Irani ubwo abanyamuryango b'inama nshingamategeko barenga makumyabiri n'ine hamwe na ba politiki b'ubu n'abasaza bagaragaye barwaye.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yanditse ibaruwa rusange ku bayobozi b'isi isaba ubufasha ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye cyiteguye kurwanya icyorezo cyatewe no kutagira amahirwe yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano Amerika yafatiye Iran. byatumye asaba Amerika gushyiraho gahunda zisanzwe z'ubuvuzi mu bihugu bikize, ku bijyanye n'ubuvuzi bw'isi, kwita ku bana bose, amafaranga y'urugendo rw'umuryango, no gutanga amafaranga menshi y'ubuzima.
Mu gihe impuguke mu bya politiki zitekereza ko Donald Trump ashobora gutsinda amatora ya perezida yo mu 2020, umubano w'ububanyi n'amahanga hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo watangiye kuzamba bitewe n'icyorezo.
" Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "" imihati yo gucecekesha u Buyapani "" nyuma y'aho u Buyapani butangarije ko abantu bose bavuye muri Koreya y'Epfo bazajya bamara ibyumweru bibiri mu kato ahantu hateganyijwe na leta. "
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, abantu bagaragaje impungenge mu gihe Perezida Moon Jae-in yasubizaga ikibazo cy'icyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yahamagariye Moon kwihagarika kubera ko bavugaga ko leta ari yo yatumye icyorezo kigabanuka, cyangwa ishimira uruhare rwayo. Annoban yatumye ibihugu byinshi bishyiraho ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rwo gusubiza.
Hari abahanga bavuze ko ibyo bishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bw'ibihugu byombi bushobora gukomeza ubutegetsi bwabwo.
Muri Hongiriya, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko yemeje ko Perezida Viktor Orban, wari kuba Perezida w'Igihugu w'Ubutegetsi bw'Ikirenga, yahagarika imirimo y'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko, kandi ko yahanisha mu gihe cy'amatora, abashinjacyaha bakomeje guhangana n'ubutabera bw'ibanze.
Icyorezo cya Koronavirusi cyateye ibibazo by'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, guhera ku kwiyongera kw'ubukene bw'ibicuruzwa n'icyorezo ku isi, kugura nabi, ibura ry'uburinganire mu masoko n'ibigo.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura ibiribwa n'imiti (FDA) cyatanze umuburo ku igabanuka ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abaguzi babyifuza cyane kubera impungenge zo kutabikwamo.
Mu turere twinshi twabonye ubwoba bwo kugura ibintu byatumaga habaho kubura ibicuruzwa by'amaduka nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku, n'amazi yo mu macupa, bituma habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa.
Ikoranabuhanga ryagiye ritera ikibazo cyo gutinda kwinjiza ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga mu bihugu by'amahanga.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, umubare w'abantu bakeneye ibikoresho byo kwirinda indwara wiyongereyeho 100%.
Ibiciro by'imiti byongerewe ku kigereranyo cy'ibiciro, bituma serivisi z'ubuvuzi zigabanuka mu mezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
