Gukaraba intoki, ubusanzwe byitwa koza intoki, ni uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki kugira ngo umuntu akureho imyanda, amavuta, udukoko cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakwiriye.
"Kugenda ukaraba intoki kenshi ukoresheje isabune ni "igihe cy'ingenzi"" mu gihe cy'amanywa, kandi bifasha mu kwirinda indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibicurane n'ibyorezo by'indwara y'ibicurane, byandurira mu myanya y'ibanga".
Abantu bashobora kwandura ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, urugero nk'iyo batanaje intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku mazuru no ku munwa.
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi ni: gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere na nyuma yo kuva mu bwiherero, nyuma yo gukaraba umwana no kumuhindurira agatambaro, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere yo guteka na nyuma yo guteka, na nyuma yo gukora ku mafi, amafi cyangwa inzu y'ubuhinzi.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune bihari, gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe ibicurane by'amazi n'ibirungo, OMS itanga inama zikurikira:
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe utegura na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo gukora ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo kumushyira mu bwiherero, kumuhanagura cyangwa kumuhindurira udupfukamunwa.
Nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ibiryo byayo, amagufwa yayo n'amafupa yayo.
Kugira isuku mu gihe umuntu ari mu bitaro cyangwa mu gihe akora ku bindi bikorwa by'ubuvuzi, ni ukwirinda umwanda.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa uburyo bwo kwivuza bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Impamvu y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo buzira kubangamira ubuzima ni ugukuraho uturemangingo duto (dusa n'udukoko dutera indwara, virusi cyangwa utundi twanduza) hamwe n'ibintu bishobora guteza indwara.
Ibyo ni iby'ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni iby'ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro cyane mu kugabanya indwara z'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo, no mu gukumira icyorezo cya diyabete n'indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Ni mu rwego rwo kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa babyariye mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki ku rugero rwiza bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu batagira amajyambere mu kureba no gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bahitanywe n'indwara z'ubuhumekero na diyabete ushobora kugabanyuka hakoreshejwe ihinduka ryihariye mu mikorere, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyi miti yoroshye cyane ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa n'iyi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Gukoresha agakingirizo ku bikoresho by'imoso bishobora kugabanya ubwandu bw'igicuri ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibi byagereranywa no guha amazi meza abakene.
48% by'indwara zo mu maraso zagabanutse bitewe no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni uburyo bwiza kandi bworoshye bwo kwirinda indwara z'ubuhumekero no kwandura indwara z'ibihaha nk'uko bikorwa mu mashuri, mu ngo no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Indwara y'impyiko, uburwayi bukomeye bw'impyiko, ni yo mpamvu y'ibanze ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'ibihaha n'iy'ubuhumekero yica abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
Nk'uko UNICEF ibivuga, gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero ni umuco kandi bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa imiti iyo ari yo yose, bikagabanya mu kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri umubare w'abagore bapfa bahitanywe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero na kimwe cya kane cy'abapfa bahitanywe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Gukaraba intoki buri gihe bijyana n'indi gahunda yo gusukura amazi nk'igice cy'ibikorwa by'amazi, isuku n'isukura (WASH).
Nanone gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma umuntu arwara impyiko (indwara y'umurava), ishobora guterwa no gukora ku muntu.
Ikibazo gito cyo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma uruhu rwangirika bitewe n'uko uruhu rwumye.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012, basanze gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutera kuribwa, kuzana impumuro mbi ku ntoki, kandi ari byo bikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi na byo bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'ihungabana (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'uruhu n'iz'akanwa: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (gushyiraho isabune, si gukodesha), nyuma yo gukaraba umwana (guhindura isahani), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo gukaraba cyangwa gukorakora inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Ubundi buryo bwo gukaraba intoki ku buryo buhoraho bugamije kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara ni nko gukaraba intoki mbere cyangwa nyuma yo gukata cyangwa gukomeretsa; nyuma yo gukora ku magufa y'inyamaswa cyangwa ku matungo; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune n'indi miti ni ibintu bikunze kugorana.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwerekanye ko ku kigereranyo cya 38.7% by'abaturage bakaraba intoki n'isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwerekanye ko Arabia Saoudite ifite igipimo kiri hejuru cya 97% cy'abaturage muri Amerika yo hagati na 77% mu gihe Ubushinwa bwo bufite igipimo kiri hasi cyane kuri 23%.
"Gahunda y'ingenzi yo kubungabunga ubuzima" yashyizweho n'ikigo gishinzwe uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'ingamba zo kubungabunga ubuzima bw'abana no kubatoza kwiga.
Gukaraba kabiri mu mwaka, bifasha gukaraba intoki buri munsi ukoresheje isabune, no gukaraba mu kanwa buri munsi ukoresheje fluorure, ni byo byibanze muri iyi gahunda yo gukaraba ku isi.
Byanatangiwe kandi muri Indoneziya.
Gukaraba mu maso udukoko duto tutabonwa n'amaso byongera ubwiza bw'uruhu iyo usukishije amazi n'isabune cyangwa ifu y'isabuni.
Intambwe ya mbere yo gukora amasabune n'ifu y'isabune yakorwaga kugira ngo bagabanye inzitizi zo gutsinda no kongera uburyo bwo gusya.
Amazi ni yo yonyine akenewe mu gukaraba uruhu, ariko si amavuta na poroteyine, bikomoka mu butaka, bidapfa gukurwa mu mazi.
Nanone kandi, icyo gikorwa cyo kwiyeza cyakorwaga hakoreshejwe amazi y'umugezi.
Kubera ko isabune y'amazi ishobora gukoreshwa igihe icyo ari cyo cyose, ishobora no gutuma haboneka mikorobe zavuye mu bikoresho byakoreshejwe mbere.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku binyabuzima bito bwerekanye ko kwanduza udusimba dukomoka ku isabune byangiza cyane mu gihe ibyo kwanduza udusimba dukomoka ku myanda.
Ikigo cya CDC cyatangaje ko uburyo bwo gukaraba amazi no kuyasuka mu mazi ari bwo bwiza cyane.
Abaturage bagirwa inama yo gukoresha amasabuni yica udukoko.
Kugeza ubu, nta kimenyetso kigaragaza ko imiti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya mikorobe cyangwa mu kurwanya mikorobe ziba mu bidukikije, ari yo ikoreshwa.
Nyamara kandi, imiti yica mikorobe irimo imiti yica mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, irimo ibintu byinshi by'ingenzi mu mikorere y'ingirabuzima fatizo.
Nubwo rero nta muntu wahitamo ko agakoko gatera indwara kagashya, birashoboka ko kaba katagira ubushobozi nk'ubwo kagaragaza.
Usibye kuba ari surfactant n'ikintu kirinda uruhu, Ibiranga ikirere birimo yacid (acide acétique, acide lactique ya acide ascorbique) nka modulateur ya PH, acide benzoic ikora antimicrobial kandi ikongera uruhu (aleo vera, vitamine, menthol, extract de plante) Ibisubizo bigufi byakozwe na kaminuza ya Oregon ishuli ry'ubuzima bw'imyororokere ko isabune isa neza nka sabune yica mikorobe irimo triclosan yo kwirinda indwara no kwica mikorobe z'intoki.
Amazi ashyushye umuntu anywa iyo agiye gukaraba intoki, nta bushyuhe buhagije kugira ngo yice mikorobe.
Iyo umubiri wawe ufite ubushyuhe buri munsi bwa dogere 37, ni bwo mikorobe zigaragara cyane.
Nyamara, amazi ashyushye, isabune ni byiza kurusha amazi akonje, amazi y'isabuni aruta kuvanaho amavuta mu butaka, ndetse n'utuntu duto cyane ijisho ntirishobora kubona.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo abantu benshi batekereza, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu bya siyansi bugaragaza ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta cyo bimaze mu birebana no kurwanya mikorobe ziba mu biganza.
