Uburyo bwo kwirinda COVID-19 ku kazi
Kugenzura ibyago byo mu kazi biterwa na COVID-19 bifasha mu kurinda aho umuntu akorera n'uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima kugira ngo amenye ibyago byo kurinda abantu kwandura icyorezo cya COVID-19 cy'icyorezo cya koronavirusi cyo mu mwaka wa 2019.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago byo mu kazi bushingiye ku miterere y'ahantu hakorerwa akazi n'aho bikorerwa, hashingiwe ku bipimo by'ibyago byo mu karere kagezweho n'icyorezo, ubukana bw'icyorezo mu baturage, n'ibyago byo kuba abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cy'ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi (OSHA), ibyago byo kwandura ku kazi biterwa no guhura n'abantu benshi hamwe n'abo bakorana, aho ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo igihe barwaye, gukaraba mu mwuka, gusukura no kwica za mikorobe mu buryo busanzwe mu gihe cy'akazi.
Mu kazi gashyirwaho ingamba zo kwirinda icyorezo harimo akazi gasaba guhura cyangwa guhura n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho ko bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'uko mu baturage hari icyorezo cyangwa bakaba baragiye mu mahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bakorana n'abaturage, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hari abantu benshi, n'ahantu hakunda kugurishwa ibintu byinshi.
Mu kwirinda ibyago byo kwandura iyi virusi muri ibi byiciro, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo gukoresha ibyuma by'umwuka bihumeka, kwambara udupfukamunwa n'ibindi bikoresho byo mu rwego rwa serivisi, mu gihe umuntu yaba yanduye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakozi bo mu rugo bagaragaye ku muntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19 bari mu kaga gakomeye, karushaho kuba hejuru mu gihe abakozi bakurikije amabwiriza yo gusuka ibyuka, cyangwa bagakusanya cyangwa bagakoresha ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19.
