Mu gihe bishoboka ko ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 bitazakurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kugenzura ni ugukora ibikoresho, gukurikirwa n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ugashyiraho uburyo bwo kwirinda.
Ubushake mu by'ubwubatsi bushingiye ku kwirengagiza abakozi ibyago bijyanye n'akazi bitagendanye n'imiterere y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba igisubizo gihenze cyashyizwe mu bikorwa.
Urwego rushinzwe igenzura rushobora guhindura imiterere y'akazi n'imikorere yabyo bisaba ko umukozi akora amasaha runaka.
Imyenda y'ubwirinzi (PPE) isa n'aho nta cyo ikora mu kurinda indwara, ariko ishobora kugabanya ubwandu.
Imyenda ya PPE yose igomba gutoranywa mbere y'uko umukozi agerwaho n'impanuka, ikagirwa neza (nk'ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero), igomba gukorerwa isuku buri gihe kandi neza, igomba gusuzumwa buri gihe, igomba guhindurwa mu gihe ifashe, igomba gukurwaho, gukaraba no gukaraba neza kugira ngo umukozi adashobora kwangirika.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi (OSHA), kuba ahantu hakorerwa imirimo hafite ibyago bike bifatwa nk'aho hari umutekano muke bitewe n'uko umukozi aba atagira aho ahurira n'abandi bakozi.
Gahunda z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zasabwe ahantu hose hakorerwa imirimo harimo gukaraba intoki buri munsi, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhumeka bufite igisenge cy'isuku n'isukura, gushyiraho ibigega by'impapuro n'ibikoresho by'isuku, gutegura gukorera mu rugo cyangwa guhindura imyanda niba ari ngombwa, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibindi bikoresho, no kwirinda isuku no kugabanya umwanda ku kazi.
Gushakisha no gushyira mu kato abantu banduye hakiri kare ni bwo buryo bwiza bwo kurinda ubuzima bw'abakozi, abakiriya n'abakozi bo mu biro.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gisaba ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero baguma mu rugo kugeza bakize, mu gihe ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero byamaze amasaha arenga 24 nta bimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero byagabanutse cyangwa nta kimenyetso cy'indwara cyakiriwe kandi ikiruhuko cy'uburwayi kiba gikwiriye, umukozi agomba kuguma mu rugo kandi akita ku murwayi kuko aba azi gahunda.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na OSHA, abantu bari mu kaga ko kwandura iyi ndwara, harimo abantu bagomba kuba hafi ya metero esheshatu (1,8 m) z'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko ikwirakwira mu baturage mu bigo by'ubucuruzi, cyangwa kubera ko umuntu yagiye mu kindi gihugu ahantu hakwirakwijwe cyane COVID-19.
