Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatanze inama ko abarwayi bashya bagomba gushyirwa mu kato ahantu hatandukanye bitewe n'uko umuntu yanduye COVID-19 cyangwa atari yo. Usibye ibikoresho bya 'PPE' bimwe na bimwe, OSHA yagiriye inama abantu bakora mu ntera y'ibirometero 6 by'ahantu, ko bakoresha ibyuma bifasha guhumeka mu gihe hari abarwayi bamenyekanye cyangwa bakekwaho kugira SARS-COV-2, n'abakora mu byiciro by'imiti ikora 'aerosol-generating procedures' (imiti ituma haboneka umwuka).
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, NIOSH yemeje ko N95 ikoreshwa mu gupima no gupima mu buryo bw'imiti yo guhumeka, mu gihe hari umutekano ushyigikiwe, harimo no gupima no gupima neza, kwiga no gupima kwa muganga.
Hari ibikoresho by'umwuka bifasha abakozi kwirinda no kurushaho kugira ubuzima bwiza. OMS ntiyemera ko hakoreshwa amakarito, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero yandura mu myanya y'ibanga.
OMS ivuga ko udupfukamunwa tw'abaganga ari ngombwa ku bakozi bo ku rwego rwo kugenzura abantu binjiye mu gihugu.
Ku bantu bahabwa ibizamini by'ubuhumekero, bakagenzura cyangwa bakagenzura umuntu ufite COVID-19 batabanje gukoresha uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza imyuka igenda mu kirere, OMS itanga inama y'uko bambara agapfukamunwa, amadarubindi, amakanzu, amakanzu y'imbere n'ibitambaro.
Iyo ikoreshwa ry'imirasire y'ubwirinzi (aerosol-generating) rikurikijwe, rishobora gusimbura ikoreshwa ry'udupfukamunwa two mu cyumba cyo kwa muganga (N95 mask) cyangwa agapfukamunwa ko mu bwoko bwa FFP2.
Dukurikije ko ibikoresho bya PPE bitakiboneka ku isi hose, OMS igisha ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ibyo bikoresho binyuze mu gutanga imiti ku buryo bworoshye, kurinda umubiri w'umuntu, kureka abafite uruhare mu kwita ku muntu ufite COVID-19 bakinjira mu cyumba, gukoresha PPE gusa mu bikorwa byihariye, gukomeza gukoresha ibyuma bifasha guhumeka neza kandi bitavanwaho mu gihe wita ku barwayi benshi bafite uburwayi bumwe, kugenzura no guhuza ibicuruzwa bya PPE, no gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu.
