Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibarura rya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, umubare w'abapfuye ku isi wari ku kigero cya 6.9% (153,822/2, 240,191) ku ya 17 Mata 2020.
Imibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere, Ibindi bipimo birimo imibare y'abana bavutse (CFR) yerekana umubare w'abantu bapimwe n'abatapimwe bapfuye.
Imibare y'abantu barwaye iyi ndwara ni iyo vuba kandi igaragaza abantu runaka barwaye iyi ndwara ariko bakira.
Nubwo abantu bose badafite abasirikare barwanya indwara, kuba hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe byo mu rwego rwa shimi bishobora gutanga ibisobanuro ku birebana n'uko abantu benshi banduzwa.
Mu cyorezo cy'indwara yo mu Butaliyani, Castiglione d'Adda, umudugudu muto w'abantu 4600, 80 (1.7%) baramaze gupfa.
Muri Genglet, iki cyorezo cyakwirakwijwe cyane mu gihe cy'ibirori by'iminsi mikuru, kandi gukwirakwira mu rubyiruko ni cyo cyateye urupfu rwinshi kandi si abantu bose bahitanwe na COVID-19 nk'uko byateganijwe.
Ariko kandi, gahunda yo kwita ku buzima y'Abadage yo ntiyari yarigeze ihinduka.
Mu Buholandi, abagera kuri 3% by'amaraso batanga ni ay'abantu bafite uburwayi, nk'uko byemezwa n'abajyanama b'ubuzima.
Abantu 69 (ni ukuvuga 0.004% by'abaturage) bagaragajwe ko bishwe na COVID-19.
Imibare y'indwara n'impfu by'abagore iratandukanye cyane mu bagabo no mu bagore.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani, bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abagabo bapfa ari munini cyane
Abagabo bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura ni abafite imyaka 50 n'abayirengeje, mu gihe abagabo n'abagore bafite ibyago byo kwandura biri ku kigero cya 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abagabo bapfa ni 2.8% naho uw'abagore ni 1.7% gusa.
Impamvu zituma habaho itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore ntizisobanutse neza ariko ibiyobyabwenge n'ibindi bintu bifitanye isano n'ubusambanyi bishobora kuba ari byo bitera iryo tandukaniro.
Imibare y'abanduye barwaye indwara z'umutima mu bagabo no mu bagore, kuba abagore batanywa itabi cyane, ndetse no kuba abagabo barwara indwara y'umuvuduko w'amaraso cyane kurusha abagore, bituma abagabo bapfa vuba.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye COVID-19 ni abagabo, naho 72% by'abapfuye bitewe na COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Kuva muri Mata 2020, leta y'Amerika ntiyigeze itandukanya igitsina mu gihe umuntu yarwara COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa na virusi nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS zigera ku bagabo n'abagore mu bihe bitandukanye.
Abaganga ni bo benshi mu bakozi b'abaganga, kandi abagore ni bo bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyo virusi.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko izina ry'icyorezo ari "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yasobanuye ko CO ihagarariye corona, VI ihagarariye virusi, D ihagarariye indwara, na 19 ihagarariye igihe iki cyorezo cyabonetse bwa mbere: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Iryo zina ryatoranyijwe kugira ngo abantu birinde gutekereza ko ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa abantu bwaba bwaravuye ahantu hamwe (urugero nko mu Bushinwa), nk'uko uburyo bwo kwita abantu mu mazina bushobora kubikora. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rikoresha izina "COVID-19" n'izina ry'indwara itera COVID-19 mu itumanaho rusange.
Iyi virusi ifitanye isano n'indwara ya corona, ikaba yitwa koronavirusi
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyadutse mu Bushinwa mu mujyi wa Wuhan, virusi n'indwara byiswe coronavirus na Wuhan coronavirus.
Muri Mutarama 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje ko 2019-nCoV na 2019-nCoV, ari amazina y'igihe gito y'icyorezo cy'ibicurane n'icyorezo cyo mu myanya y'ibanze, hashingiwe ku mahame yo mu 2015 yo gukoresha ahantu hazwi ho kuvura indwara z'ibyorezo.
COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 byiswe izina ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ubushobozi buke mu buryo bwatanzwe, inganda zimwe zicapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka no guhumeka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byasabwaga guhita byakira ibyuma by'umwuka, kandi umukozi w'ibitaro ataha igihe, ibyuma byo mu nzu byasohotse mu ijoro birekura ibyuma by'umwuka 100 bikenewe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, inyigisho z'ubuhakanyi, inkuru z'ibinyoma zivuga ku nkomoko, ingano, kwirinda n'ibindi bintu by'icyorezo byatangiye gukwirakwizwa cyane kuri interineti.
Abantu bashobora kwanduza izo ndwara izindi nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku ngurube, inkoko n'inkoko ntibyageze ku kimenyetso cya virusi.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe na Leta bivura iyo ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga kuri COVID-19 bugikorwa n'inzego za leta, amashami y'ubushakashatsi n'amashami y'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije igerageza ry'inkingo enye zitewe n'ubwandu, ryitwa SOLIDARITY Trial.
Nubwo nta muti w'iyo ndwara uhari, hari inzego zitandukanye zigerageza kuyirwanya.
Igikorwa cyo gukingira SARS-CoV gikoreshwa mu buryo bwa nyuma kubera ko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwanduza abantu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo kumenya aho icyo kintu kiri.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abashakashatsi bari bafite intego yo kuvanaho iyo virusi.
Gukoresha bene iyi mikorobe, yaba idafite ubukana cyangwa yapfuye, byerekana ko umuntu afite ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19 mu gihe yihutira kubukingira.
Icyiciro cya kabiri, cyo kurwanya indwara, kirimo gukorwa kugira ngo haboneke inkingo zizafasha kurwanya zimwe mu ndwara.
Ku birebana na SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine ya S-Spike ifasha virusi kugira uruhare mu kongera poroteyine ya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni ubwandu bushingiye kuri aside ya nikleyiki (DNA cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo kuvura ubwandu).
Inkingo za buri bwoko zigomba kubanza gupimwa kugira ngo harebwe niba nta ngaruka mbi cyangwa niba nta cyo zangiza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, ni ukuvuga ko inkingo za mbere z'uruganda rw'inkingo z'abantu bane zikorerwa mu mujyi wa Seattle.
Urukingo rw'agakoko ruba rugizwe n'uduce tw'umubiri tw'umubiri udatewe n'agakoko gatera iyi ndwara. Hari inama yatanzwe yo gukoresha umuti urwanya SARS-COV-2 nk'uburyo bwo gukingira, ariko hakaba impaka.
Muri Mata 2020, ibitaro byagize abarwayi barenga 300 bari mu bizamini.
Hari uburyo burindwi bwo gupima ubwirinzi bw'ubuvuzi bw'ibicurane, harimo n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kuri hydrochloricquine na chloroquine.
Ubushakashatsi bw'Abashinwa ku rukingo, bwari bumaze kugera ku cyiciro cya cyenda cy'igerageza ku rukingo rwa Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi kubera ibibazo by'uburwayi mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Mata.
Gusuzuma byimbitse iterambere ry'ubuvuzi bw'amaraso ku miti ya COVID-19 n'imiti igerageza iriho. kuva muri Mata 2020. Imiti myinshi yo kurwanya virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, looinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritomavir ifatanyije na betaferon.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko remdesivir ifite ubushobozi bwo kuvura, guhera muri Werurwe 2020.
Abantu benshi bari barwaye indwara ziterwa n'imiti ya Remdesivir, barakize cyane.
Ibizamini byo mu rwego rwa Phase III birakorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa no mu Butaliyani. Chloroquine yakoreshwaga mu kuvura malariya, Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa mu 2020 bwashyizwe mu bikorwa mu cyumweru cya mbere.
Icyakora, hari abantu benshi bakomeje kubaza kugira ngo barebe niba ibyo bisobanuro ari ukuri.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Koreya n'u Bushinwa bagaragaje ko gukoresha chloroquine ari byiza.
Ariko, Kaminuza ya Wuhan mu byerekeye indwara, ivuga ko gukoresha gramu imwe ku munsi ari byiza, mu gihe gukoresha ebyiri ku munsi bishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze amabwiriza yihutirwa yo kwemeza ko hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine zishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura abantu barwaye COVID-19. Amabwiriza y'Abashinwa yo mu cyiciro cya 7 yashyizwemo interferon, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere y'aho bwagaragaje ko gufata igipimo kinini cya ribavirine bifite akamaro mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Hakozwe ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze ku ikoreshwa rya Nitazoxanide mu bushakashatsi nyuma yo kugaragaza ko idashobora kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gutangiza poroteyine ya spike ya mbere ikorwa na serine 2 ya protéinase yo mu nkingo (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi mu kwanduza SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu kwanduzanya na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku ikorwa rya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na koba na azithromycin bufite imbogamizi zikomeye zituma inzego z'ubuvuzi zititabira gukoresha ubundi buryo bwo kuvura hadakoreshejwe ubundi bushakashatsi. Oseltamivir ntabwo ikora mu gupima SARS-CoV-2 kandi nta ruhare izwi ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Igitutu cya sitokineti gishobora kuba ikibazo iyo COVID-19 ikomeje gufata intera ndende.
Ubushinwa bwashyize tocizumab mu mabwiriza yo kuvura nyuma y'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe.
Ni igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya 2 ryakozwe n'abantu baturuka mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ingaruka ku bantu bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Uretse gupima amaraso mu buryo bwa serumu ferritine mu rwego rwo kumenya ko hari sitokine zitera indwara, ubu bushakashatsi bugamije kumenya niba hari izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo zishobora guhitana abantu bafite ubwandu bwa virusi.
FDA yemeje interleukin-6 receptor antagonist y'inyongera ishingiye ku isuzuma ry'imiterere y'imiterere yo kuvura indwara ya sitokini itera steroid refractory ifata ibimenyetso byatewe n'impamvu itandukanye, CAR T iseri yo kuvura, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu nta kimenyetso cy'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushake bw'imiti ya tocilizumab ngo cyerekane ko ishobora gutera indwara ya CRS.
Kwanduza no gukusanya abasirikare b'umubiri bavuye ku ndwara ya COVID-19 mu bantu basuzumwa mu buryo butari ubw'urukingo.
Iyi sisitemu yagerageje muri SARS ariko nta musaruro ivanze.
Igisubizo cyo kugabanya ubukana bw'iyi virusi ni ukongera ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Hari n'izindi nzira zishobora kuboneka, nk'izifashishwa mu kurwanya indwara, urugero nk'ubumara bugera mu ngirabuzimafatizo bukayandura, n'uburyo bwo kuyirinda.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kongerera abasirikare b'umubiri ubushobozi, urugero nko gukoresha agakingirizo ka monoclonal karimo kongerwa.
Gukora serumu y'indwara, ikubiyemo igice cy'amaraso y'umuntu yanduye kandi irimo imiti yica mikorobe yo muri iyi virusi, ishobora kongerwaho kugirango ikoreshwe hakiri kare.
Koronavirusi ni indwara ifata ibinyabiziga by'abantu benshi.
